2:44 PM case called. Prosecuting attorney Trenton John Piltz in court for the State of Wisconsin.  Defendant Dennis A Granlund in court.  Attorney Bryant S Plank appeared by video for Dennis A Granlund.

State makes argument for bind over. Defense makes an argument against bind over. 
Court finds probable cause and binds matter over to Branch 3 for ARGN.
